Class CallCard

  • java.lang.Object
    • FrameLayout
      • org.sipdroid.sipua.phone.CallCard
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CallerInfoAsyncQuery.OnQueryCompleteListener, ContactsAsyncHelper.OnImageLoadCompleteListener

    public class CallCard
extends FrameLayout
implements CallerInfoAsyncQuery.OnQueryCompleteListener, ContactsAsyncHelper.OnImageLoadCompleteListener
    "Call card" UI element: the in-call screen contains a tiled layout of call cards, each representing the state of a current "call" (ie. an active call, a call on hold, or an incoming call.)
